==制作==
导演[[贝尼特·米勒|贝尼特·米勒]]从2010年开始构思这部电影<ref>{{cite news |first=Jeff |last=Sneider |date=September 30, 2012 |title=Megan Ellison to finance 'Foxcatcher' |magazine=Variety |url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118043717 |accessdate=October 20, 2012 |archive-date=2021-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210218013344/https://variety.com/2011/film/news/megan-ellison-to-finance-foxcatcher-1118043717/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="feinberg">{{cite news |first=Scott |last=Feinberg |date=August 15, 2014 |title='Foxcatcher' Jumps to Sony Pictures Classics; Release Date Set |magazine=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/race/foxcatcher-jumps-sony-pictures-classics-602726 |accessdate=August 16, 2013 |archive-date=2014-06-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140608234056/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/race/foxcatcher-jumps-sony-pictures-classics-602726 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2012年10月15日在[[宾夕法尼亚州|宾夕法尼亚州]]开拍<ref name="serafini">{{cite news |first=Kristina |last=Serafini |date=October 17, 2012 |title=Film crews back in Sewickley area |newspaper=[[Tribune-Review|Tribune-Review]] |url=http://triblive.com/neighborhoods/2780178-74/sewickley-movie-road-mcdaniel-crews-film-edgeworth-filmed-heights-shot |accessdate=October 18, 2012 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6CzAN8cO5?url=http://triblive.com/neighborhoods/2780178-74/sewickley-movie-road-mcdaniel-crews-film-edgeworth-filmed-heights-shot |archivedate=2012-12-17 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，2013年1月杀青。

==评价==
影片在[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]保持87%的好评率<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/foxcatcher/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-05-22 |archive-date=2014-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140519190729/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/foxcatcher/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。一些评论认为[[史提夫·加維|史提夫·加維]]将会获得[[奥斯卡最佳男主角|奥斯卡最佳男主角]]提名<ref>{{cite news |last=Shoard |first=Catherine |url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/2014/may/19/cannes-acclaim-for-steve-carell-in-foxcatcher-sparks-oscars-hopes |title=Cannes acclaim for Steve Carell in Foxcatcher prompts Oscars tips |date=19 May 2014 |accessdate=20 May 2014 |publisher=The Guardian |archive-date=2014-05-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140522053940/http://www.theguardian.com/film/2014/may/19/cannes-acclaim-for-steve-carell-in-foxcatcher-sparks-oscars-hopes |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[新浪|新浪]]影评认为：“电影大部分在室内拍摄，没有阳光的灰色画面，突出了沉重压抑的气氛。片中对人性阴暗一面的刻画，带著浓厚的[[莎士比亚|莎士比亚]]悲剧性质。史蒂夫-卡瑞尔饰演的约翰-杜邦无疑为本片加添了不少深度，他说话的声音和神态，令人想起发动第二次[[伊拉克战争|伊拉克战争]]的美国前总统[[小布什|小布什]]。它是一部发人深省的电影，尤其是对金钱至上的美国社会的尖锐批评。它探讨了许多心理和社会伦理方面的问题。金钱和权力歪曲人性，令人堕落的可怕力量，早在上世纪90年代就已如此，目前这种情况只有变本加厉，而且蔓延到全世界。这部在手法上很传统的影片，由于结构严谨，演员出色，导演对真实事件抽丝剥茧的艺术处理结果，从头到尾都能维持着一股张力，是一部在各个方面都很出色的电影。”<ref >{{cite web |url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/r/i/2014-05-22/07184146011.shtml |language= |title=《狐狸猎手》：手法传统结构严谨演员出色 |publisher=新浪娱乐 |date=2014年5月22日 |accessdate= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140522110351/http://ent.sina.com.cn/r/i/2014-05-22/07184146011.shtml |archive-date=2014年5月22日 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

馬克·舒爾茨本人則對電影有許多批評，他認為導演扭曲了事實，對電影情節影射杜邦跟他之間有同性戀曖昧之情，特別不满<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://twitter.com/MarkSchultzy/status/549710019684347905 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-01-13 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305040753/https://twitter.com/MarkSchultzy/status/549710019684347905 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://uk.businessinsider.com/foxcatcher-movie-slammed-by-mark-schultz-2015-1?r=US |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-01-13 |archive-date=2015-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150110045112/http://uk.businessinsider.com/foxcatcher-movie-slammed-by-mark-schultz-2015-1?r=US |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/2015/jan/02/mark-schultz-attacks-gay-relationship-in-wrestling-biopic-foxcatcher |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-01-13 |archive-date=2015-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150111023659/http://www.theguardian.com/film/2015/jan/02/mark-schultz-attacks-gay-relationship-in-wrestling-biopic-foxcatcher |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

